WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.099 --> 00:00:06.399
Today on our 2014 Chevy Silverado, well be
installing the Torklift Custom Frame-Mounted

00:00:06.399 --> 00:00:14.090
Camper Tie-Downs, part number TLC2214 for
the front of the pickup bed.

00:00:14.090 --> 00:00:20.430
Well first locate the 3-hole strap bar, a
3.5 inch bolt and star washer.

00:00:20.430 --> 00:00:27.010
Well take the bolt, feed it through the over
hold here at the end of the bar.

00:00:27.010 --> 00:00:31.370
Then well take the strap and feed it around
the front bed cross member perch.

00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:34.699
This will be the first one closest to the
cabin of the truck.

00:00:34.699 --> 00:05:59.080
Before we place our bracket up, well need
to loosen up our wiring harness here.

